title: Borderlands 2 WattleGobbler By NoSteam
description:
This will update even the Skidrow versions of borderlands 2 to
now include the new Ravenous Wattle Gobbler DLC.
This worked just fine for my skidrow version, it did not mess up
my saved games.
I didn't see anything for the pc posted yet at the time of this
upload.
This is my first share, so please no flaming if I messed anything up
while trying to help others.

Download, run the nosteam exe and point it to your borderlands 2 folder
for install. Then play, it was that simple for me.
